class hierarchy:

Strip
    Sequence
        Scene
            Shot:
                -image or images for animation.
            Dialogue;
                Text
                    -color
                    -style
                    -body of text (string).
      
outside world is responsible for passing keyboard events to the "Strip".
The Strip class is an html canvas wrapper....  

Strip:
    loadSequence()
    loadSequenceFromFile()

    events:
        END
        SEQUENCE_LOADED

    actions/navigation:
        NEXT
        PREVIOUS
        TO_END_OF_SCENE
        TO_PREVIOUS_SCENE

